text: Eslarn is a market town and municipality in Neustadt an der Waldnaab in Bavaria in Germany. == Neighbouring communities == The neighbouring communities clockwise: Waidhaus, Rozvadov, Třemešné, Bělá nad Radbuzou, Schönsee, Oberviechtach, Moosbach (Oberpfalz) and Pleystein. ==References== Category:Neustadt an der Waldnaab (district)
title: Eslarn
